Package pizzaProgram.dataObjects

This package contains classes that encapsulates various data from the database, like Dishes, Customers etc.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Customer A data object that holds information about a customer in the database
Dish Class encapsulating all information about any given dish on the restaurants menu.
Extra A data object that holds data about an Extra in the database
Order Represents an order from the database
OrderDish Represents a dish from the database that is a part of an order
Setting A data object representing a setting in the database
UnaddedCustomer A data object that represents a customer that has not yet been added to the database
UnaddedOrder A class that represents an order that has not yet been added to the database
UnaddedOrderDish A data object representing a dish that has not yet been added to the database
